</a>
</li>
<li>
<a title="Democrats Will Keep the States Closed to Tank the Economy and Take Down Trump - 32" href="/columnists/toddstarnes/2020/04/17/democrats-will-keep-the-states-closed-to-tank-the-economy-and-take-down-trump-n2567117">
