 <div class="mpw">
<ul class="list-unstyled">
<li>
<a title="Hold onto your HATS! Brit Hume shares fact-filled thread on study showing COVID fatality rate just bottomed out to influenza levels - 45" href="https://twitchy.com/samj-3930/2020/04/17/hold-onto-your-hats-brit-hume-shares-fact-filled-thread-on-study-showing-covid-fatality-rate-just-bottomed-out-to-influenza-levels/">
<span class="mpw__story">Hold onto your HATS! Brit Hume shares fact-filled thread on study showing COVID fatality rate just bottomed out to influenza levels</span>
</a>
<div class="mpw__domain" style="color:#F27B21;">
Twitchy
</div>
